title: Black (2006) XBOX.iso
description:
Black is an explosion-filled first-person shooter from Criterion Games, the company responsible for bringing explosions to driving games with the Burnout series. Like the Burnout games, Black packs in a lot of firepower. It seems like something's blowing up every minute or two, and this helps the game make an absolutely killer first impression.

Tested on my XBOX with softmod.

Have a blast!

Btw: this game is for the XBOX one.
